      ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iWMx4H9wW9kD07nO7"><p>Frequently asked questions</p></div
      ><div class="iVfYfbfiPFDax3fz5" data-instant-type="accordion-container" data-is-first-open="true" data-is-multi-open-enabled="false"
        ><div data-state="open" class="iWQ8ikXS83IWRsetk" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
          ><button class="iAuJB5jkTJd9YZWJU" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text ik4L3oW2ZcT2DCwdd"><h3>who writes the stories?</h3></div
            ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="io88IdcRqRErNwI6C">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                <title>caret-down</title><path d="M213.66,101.66l-80,80a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-80-80A8,8,0,0,1,53.66,90.34L128,164.69l74.34-74.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
              </svg></div></button
          ><div class="i8xARqIOcFCyvlqL4" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text ilJWmJxy4Pz1p9EV0"><p>We have a team of former educators (elementary and secondary) who still remain passionate about educating the next generation. They know exactly what styles of language to use to help further your kids education.</p></div></div
          ></div
        ><div data-state="closed" class="iRxu0a6Rqd4yAAGCz" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
          ><button class="ik9y6n9PCkUrSWcst" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iuTUomjazlVUiedqk"><h3>What topics can i expect?</h3></div
            ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="i845A0YXUbUbWifFV">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                <title>caret-down</title><path d="M213.66,101.66l-80,80a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-80-80A8,8,0,0,1,53.66,90.34L128,164.69l74.34-74.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
              </svg></div></button
          ><div class="iNx4NUna3ISlFOb9U" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iyRQA1O9q1u2chCiU"
              ><p>All our stories are based on real historical events, science, or world concepts. Everything is adjusted so that its suitable and engaging for young children. Some upcoming stories include:</p
              ><ul
                ><li><p>&#8220;Man Lands on The Moon&#8221;</p></li
                ><li><p>&#8220;United States Signs the Declaration of Independence&#8221;</p></li
                ><li><p>&#8220;Benjamin Franklin Captures the Power of Lightning&#8221;</p></li></ul
              ></div
            ></div
          ></div
        ><div data-state="closed" class="ix47m4BJDpmtTCgz0" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
          ><button class="iCLBeNfMsLDdVwBue" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text itGwbPJ8WwqvSrRjp"><h3>when will the product arrive?</h3></div
            ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="i6gbXkWjnLSFADHjA">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                <title>caret-down</title><path d="M213.66,101.66l-80,80a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-80-80A8,8,0,0,1,53.66,90.34L128,164.69l74.34-74.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
              </svg></div></button
          ><div class="iMMhUeJXSyP3bThGV" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iv9aKzsSIAMsHnvC5"><p>We ship in batches of 3 editions at a time. After your first order, you will receive the first batch in 4-5 business days. Subsequent batches will arrive 3 months after that.</p></div></div
          ></div
        ><div data-state="closed" class="i4406u7ILXm4qVYrO" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
          ><button class="iXuhZjFaLBShDjWAJ" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iqqMb5uSMscz1z4ih"><h3>what age range is it suitable for?</h3></div
            ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iUjVFP1NnF2ZpQH2D">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                <title>caret-down</title><path d="M213.66,101.66l-80,80a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-80-80A8,8,0,0,1,53.66,90.34L128,164.69l74.34-74.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
              </svg></div></button
          ><div class="ieb0uyxEJoYlmO0S4" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text irSVFqT9mLQgLoIe8"><p>The Bedtimes is a highly visual format, which means the youngest learners (ranging from 8-12 years old) can benefit from the exposure.</p></div></div
          ></div
        ><div data-state="closed" class="iK0DVO3GfgzQ7vK7X" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
          ><button class="ig1ufjtTYdPVKAOt9" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text i4HO0hDz6eL9ws2CO"><h3>How do you choose what topics to write about?</h3></div
            ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iPnpceRCjoU6oWvmf">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                <title>caret-down</title><path d="M213.66,101.66l-80,80a8,8,0,0,1-11.32,0l-80-80A8,8,0,0,1,53.66,90.34L128,164.69l74.34-74.35a8,8,0,0,1,11.32,11.32Z"></path>
              </svg></div></button
          ><div class="iUM83wJrpEfUJD4f2" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
            ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iA589RFjTVifLWLwg"><p>The world is already full of amazing stories. Each month, we look back in time into history, and look for the events which have helped shape our world today.</p><p>We prioritise stories which will help your child make sense of the world – useful scientific discoveries, important historical events, and events which help expose them to new cultures.</p><p>And of course – we listen to our communities suggestions.</p></div></div
          ></div
        ></div
